headline: Federal Realty Investment Trust Releases Tax Status of 2025 Distributions
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE: FRT) released today the Federal income tax treatment for 2025 distributions to holders of its Common Shares of Beneficial Interest (NYSE: FRT) and its 5.000% Series C Cumulative Redeemable Preferred Shares (NYSE: FRT.PRC).
